Nodes.Comment:
Start
Buy on the TP 25 [Baraccuda Meat] to complete one of the Hearts

Do the event if it's up,
or train with the Soldiers, you can fight more than one at a time,
kill Rats on the way
Just clear the concentrated Tar on the surface
If you hate Jumping-puzzles take the alternative route
If the gate is blocking you go on your Springer and hop over it
Kill stuff and pick up (weapon-swap) Truffles
Spam the dialog till you're done
Destroy the bushes, pick up (weapon-swap) the berries they drop and kill stuff (not the moas)
If you didn't kill all 4 bushes you need more than that
Raptor-jump from the edge or glide
Turn in the 25 [Barracuda Meat] bought on the TP
Pick up a Grenade Kit, remount, get to the next WP than port back
Kill stuff with the Grenades you earlier picked up
You can (weapon-swap) destroy the Power Sources
If you don't have PoF get the POI than turn around and take the alt route to your left

DetachedNodes.Comment: Get the vista after the WP
Get the vista than WP back here

This Route is made with Mounts in mind.
To follow the exact Route you need Raptor 3 and Springer 3. \Alternative routes are marked with these pink cubes.
Go out of Combat, get movement speed and glide around the corner
